### Build-a-Bank · Step 7 · AOP audit aspect + the Phase-A capstone slice
### Start spring-lab:  ./mvnw -pl playground/spring-lab spring-boot:run   (defaults to port 8080)
### Watch the app log: every call to an @Audited method prints "AUDIT ▶ … / AUDIT ✔ …".

@host = http://localhost:8080

### List all accounts (audited) — 200 + JSON array
GET {{host}}/api/accounts
Accept: application/json

### Fetch one account (audited) — 200 + JSON
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/1
Accept: application/json
# curl: curl -i http://localhost:8080/api/accounts/1

### Missing account — clean 404
GET {{host}}/api/accounts/999
Accept: application/json
